  "data": {
    "title": "CallHippo: What It Is and Why Sales Teams Rely on It",
    "excerpt": "CallHippo is a virtual phone system with numbers from 50+ countries, call recording, IVR, and sales analytics. Here's what it is and how it works.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/what-is-callhippo.jpg",
        "alt": "CallHippo: What It Is and Why Sales Teams Rely on It",
        "filename": "what-is-callhippo.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your sales team handles dozens or hundreds of calls every day, you already know the frustration: dropped calls, missed follow-ups, zero visibility into what your reps are actually saying to prospects. CallHippo solves those problems with a cloud-based phone system that gives your team professional numbers, powerful analytics, and the kind of call infrastructure that used to require an entire IT department.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've spent time exploring CallHippo's platform, and what struck me most is how it takes something traditionally complicated—business telephony—and makes it genuinely accessible. Whether you're a five-person startup or a mid-size company with remote reps across continents, this tool meets you where you are.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me walk you through exactly what CallHippo is, what makes it stand out, and whether it fits your team's workflow.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Exactly Is CallHippo?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At its core, CallHippo is a virtual phone system designed for sales and support teams. Instead of relying on physical desk phones or PBX hardware, everything runs through the cloud. Your reps can make and receive business calls from their laptops, smartphones, or tablets—wherever they happen to be working.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "But \"virtual phone system\" undersells what CallHippo actually delivers. The platform includes:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Local and toll-free numbers from 50+ countries",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", so your business can establish a local presence in markets around the world without opening a single office.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automatic call recording",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that captures every conversation for training, compliance, and quality assurance.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "IVR (Interactive Voice Response)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that routes callers to the right department or agent using customizable menu trees.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Conversation analytics",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " powered by AI, which transcribes calls and surfaces insights about talk time, sentiment, keywords, and rep performance.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A parallel dialer",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that lets reps call multiple numbers simultaneously, dramatically increasing connect rates for outbound teams.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Think of it as the entire telephony backbone for your business, delivered as a subscription software with no hardware headaches.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
