      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Standout Features You Won't Find Everywhere",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Plenty of virtual phone tools exist. What makes CallHippo worth your attention? A few features genuinely stood out during my review.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Voice Agent",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo recently introduced an AI-powered voice agent that can handle inbound calls autonomously. It speaks naturally, answers common questions, captures lead information, and transfers complex queries to human reps. For teams that receive high volumes of routine calls—appointment confirmations, order status checks, basic FAQ inquiries—this feature alone can free up hours of agent time every week.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The AI Voice Agent doesn't replace your team. It handles the repetitive stuff so your reps can focus on conversations that actually require a human touch.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Omnichannel Inbox",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo isn't just about phone calls. Their Omnichannel Inbox consolidates voice calls, WhatsApp messages, and other channels into a single interface. Your agents see the full conversation history regardless of which channel the customer used. No more switching between tabs or losing context when a prospect moves from WhatsApp to a phone call.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "WhatsApp Business API Integration",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For teams that communicate heavily via WhatsApp (especially in markets like Latin America, Europe, or Southeast Asia), CallHippo's native WhatsApp Business API integration is a major win. You can send and receive messages, automate responses, and manage conversations alongside your phone activity—all within the same platform.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Conversation Intelligence",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every recorded call gets automatically transcribed and analyzed. CallHippo's AI identifies patterns: which talk tracks lead to closed deals, which objections come up most frequently, and which reps need coaching on specific skills. Sales managers get dashboards that turn raw call data into actionable coaching insights.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/callhippo-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For a deeper dive into what's new, check out our guide on ",
            "marks": []
