          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is CallHippo Built For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo works across industries, but certain teams will get outsized value from the platform.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Outbound Sales Teams",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your reps make dozens of calls daily, the parallel dialer and local number provisioning are game-changers. Reps connect with more prospects in less time, and those prospects are more likely to answer when they see a familiar area code.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Remote and Distributed Teams",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo's cloud architecture means location doesn't matter. A rep in Lisbon uses the same system as a rep in Austin. Calls route intelligently based on availability, time zone, or skill set. Supervisors monitor performance in real time from a unified dashboard.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "International Businesses",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Getting local numbers in 50+ countries without setting up foreign offices? That's the kind of operational flexibility that lets small companies punch above their weight. If you're expanding into new markets, CallHippo removes one of the biggest logistical headaches.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Customer Support Teams",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "IVR, call queuing, and the omnichannel inbox make CallHippo a strong fit for support teams that need to handle high call volumes professionally. Callers reach the right agent quickly, and nothing falls through the cracks.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Growing Startups and SMBs",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You don't need a massive budget or dedicated IT staff to deploy CallHippo. The platform scales with you—start with a few numbers and basic features, then add products as your team grows.",
