            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The conversation intelligence and AI Voice Agent aren't gimmicks. They address real pain points—coaching reps at scale, handling call overflow, and surfacing insights buried in hours of recordings.",
