    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/callhippo.com as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). Smiling sales team wearing headsets in a modern open office, with floating holographic phone icons and a world map showing connection lines between countries. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What is CallHippo and what does it do?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo is a cloud-based virtual phone system for sales and support teams. It provides business phone numbers from over 50 countries, automatic call recording, IVR (Interactive Voice Response), AI-powered conversation analytics, a parallel dialer for outbound calling, and an omnichannel inbox that combines voice and messaging. Teams can make and receive calls from laptops or smartphones without traditional hardware.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does CallHippo cost?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo offers transparent subscription pricing with no hidden fees. They have multiple plans ranging from Essential (for low call volumes) to Pro Suite (for high-volume teams), plus standalone products like WhatsApp Business API and AI Voice Agent. A 10-day free trial is available with no credit card required, so you can test the platform before committing.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is CallHippo good for remote sales teams?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes—CallHippo was built with distributed teams in mind. Because it's entirely cloud-based, reps can make and receive business calls from anywhere using their laptop or smartphone. Supervisors monitor performance through a unified dashboard, calls route intelligently based on availability and time zones, and everyone accesses the same system regardless of location.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
